{"title":"沿着图们江","authors":["周必忠"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":11,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着图们江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周必忠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着图们江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走马来站岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山水水如彩图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印在战士心坎上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江右——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠岭映红日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧水飘纱帐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农家女儿采野果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌唱得秋色旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火车催动千里马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车车山珍向平壤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江左——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沃野泛金波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿树绕田庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧童横笛声声吹："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿云破雾露青天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照遍东南西北方……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着图们江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走马来站岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山水画图印心坎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士心头潮水涨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想昔日——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图们江水来饮马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白头山石磨刀光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林海雪原杀敌寇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清川草岭斩豺狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理凝铸手足情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血浇开红花香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看今朝——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福常似江水流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活如花情更长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携手建设理想国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁肩傲骨斗风霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人胆敢来动土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士手中有钢枪！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}